Package app

Class TravelPackage

  • java.lang.Object
    • app.TravelPackage
  • public class TravelPackage
extends java.lang.Object
    The TravelPackage file contains all the travel plans to be used by the Yatra system. It can manipulate and modify travel plans and its components.
